msgid ""
"The full worked example for the overflow construct: 64-by-64 to 128-bit "
"multiplication via the high half, and addition with explicit carry-out "
"propagation for chained multi-digit arithmetic. Course coverage: Chapter 23 "
"introduces the construct; this document is the full technique."
msgstr ""

