msgid ""
"`stddsl::Math` and `stddsl::Audio` require the `floats` cargo feature. "
"`stddsl::Shell` requires the `shell` feature, which adds a `std` dependency "
"and is therefore incompatible with `no_std` builds. The `keleusma-cli` crate "
