#: src/SECURITY_POLICY.md:111
msgid ""
"Generate the head office's Ed25519 signing keypair. Keep the seed at the "
"head office. Distribute the public key to each workstation."
msgstr ""

#: src/SECURITY_POLICY.md:112
msgid "Install the `keleusma-cli` binary on each workstation."
