"position and the supplied keypress, then route the returned action through "
"the same per-actor resolver that handles monster actions. Returns 0 to "
"continue the turn, 1 if stairs were descended, 2 if the exit on floor one "
"hundred was reached, 3 if the player died."
msgstr ""

