#: src/METRICS.md:9
msgid ""
"All numbers measured on a single Apple M1 (`arm64-apple-darwin23`) host, May "
"2026. Each runner executed the same conceptual workload: load the runtime, "
"parse-or-load a trivial program, print the integer 42, exit. Five runs per "
"runner; the typical mid-range value is reported."
